manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

Each decentralized oracle network consists of independent node operators. In the Chainlink network, each node verifies the accuracy of external real-world data, aggregates them using an agreed-upon method, and delivers them to smart contracts that requested for the data.
This helps makes smart contracts useful for entities like financial institutions, decentralized finance projects, agricultural companies, or any data-driven companies. LINK is a utility token used to pay for data queries and is soon to be used as collateral for service agreements.

playstore_details.title: Bitazza - Bitcoin/Cryptocurrency Exchange & Wallet
playstore_details.description:
Discover the next-level Cryptocurrency trading experience on Thailand SEC-licensed Crypto Exchange. Buy & sell Crypto, even the latest DeFi tokens;
BTC - Bitcoin
ETH - Ethereum
XRP - Ripple
XLM - Stellar
UNI - Uniswap
YFI - yearn.finance
OMG - OMG Network
LINK - Chainlink
BNT - Bancor Network
SNX - Synthetix
REN - Ren Project
AAVE - Aave
ALPHA - Alpha Finance Lab
BAL - Balancer
SUSHI - SushiSwap
CRV - Curve DAO
MKR - Maker
GRT - The Graph
xNXM - Nexus Mutual
and other stable coins!

Regulated License
Bitazza has been awarded the Digital Asset Broker license regulated by Thailand’s SEC and issued by the Ministry of Finance.

Simple Interface 
User-friendly experience that gives access to your portfolio, market data, community, and updates anytime, anywhere, with Tradingview integrated.

Pay, Receive, Share
Receive, transfer, or pay with Crypto! With immediate fiat conversion, Bitazza’s Crypto wallet is accepted by multiple retail partners and merchants. Transact with other coins wallet smoothly through blockchain.

Deep Liquidity
Access a deep liquidity pool with leading crypto exchanges around the world, ensuring the best prices on the go, compare prices in one place.

Optimized Security
Fully regulated by SEC Thailand and secured by Ledger Vault with $150 million insurance.

24/7 Customer Support 
Reach the support you need via live chat or phone call. Any time of the day, anywhere you are.

Bitazza Mobile Application. Freedom In Your Hands.
Download Bitazza’s mobile app and start trading today!
